org.turkudragons.SpaceHunter

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.turkudragons.SpaceHunter.Collider
      • org.turkudragons.SpaceHunter.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Active, Visible

    public class Item
extends Collider
implements Active, Visible
    Class of all collectable items in the game. Holds information of which type of item it is and how much does it hold items. Constructor takes care of how big amount of ammo or health is included. If it is not declared in the constructor which type of item is needed then a random item is dropped to the x and y coordinates.
    Author:
    Pasi Toivanen
